My Introspection 
aaj mene bahut socha or me ye ab batana chahta hu ki mene aaj kya socha hai 

aaj me un bato ki depth tak gaya hu jisse mujhme ego aai thi 
is bare me to me pahle hi baat kar chuka hu ki mere ander ego kaha se aai 
thi mene yah to kah diya tha ki yah ego mere gar se mere ghar walo ki wajah 
se aai hai 
lekin jab me aaj or bhi depth tak gaya to mene jana ki yah create kaha se hui hai
mere ander ego kahi na kahi mere dosto ki vajah se bhi aai hai 
for example me jab 10th me tha to me ek bilkul sidha sadha ladka tha jaha me kabhi 
bhi kisi ko bura ya nicha nahi dikhaya karta tha but jab me class me accha karne laga
or science ke subject me or bhi jyada accha karne laga tab mere friend mujhse kaha karte the ki
yaar tu bhaut accha kar raha hai or kahi na kahi mere man me yah baat beth gai thi ki 
ab to mere se uper koi nahi hai koi bhi class me mujhse accha nahi 
or fir dhire dhire karke mene un logo ko nicha dikhana suru kiya jinse me jalta tha 
yah kah kar ki tumhe to kuch bhi nahi ata hai or apne hi ghamand me rahne laga 
jiski vajah se mere dost bhi mujhse naraaj se rahne lage or kuch dost meri chaplusi karne 
lage mujhse puchna or mera homwork dekh kar copy karna jisse kahi na kahi mere ander vo 
ego apne aap build hone lagi 

itna sab sochne ke baad mene un bato par gor kiya ki me un logo se jalta hi kyu tha 
kya me vo cheje nahi kar pata tha jo cheje vo log kar pate hai or fir jab me thoda or depth me jata hu to pata chalta hai ki gi ha kahi na kahi yah bhi mudda hai ki me unse isi karan jalta tha ki me unse ek samy me piche tha vo log kuch bhi kiya karte the vo mujhe nahi bataya karte the 
jiski vajah se me unse jalne laga or dhire dhire jab me sikhne laga to mene us chej ko apne under 
ek ego ki tarah paal liya or logo ke sath vahi behaviour karne laga jo mujhe accha lagata tha 
or me unki koi baat bhi nahi mana karta tha agar koi kahta tha ki aslam aaj hume ye subject ki study karna hai to me kahta tha ki nahi aaj hum kuch or padhenge or ye mere undre ka ego tha 

jo ab mujhe feel hua hai ki mere under ego hai 
or ha mene yah bhi socha hai ki me is ego ko kese hata sakta hu
isme sabse pahli cheez yah bhi hai ki humare samne ek pura pahaad hai 
or us pahad ka size kitna bada hai or uske samne me kitna cota hu jab vo pahad itna bada hai to me to uske samne kuch bhi nahi hu or is universe me kine badi badi cheze hai jiske samne to me such me kuch bhi nahi hu isliye age se jab bhi mre under ego aayegi me humeshsa apne aap se pahle yah question karunga ki me kya hua or me in bato ko yaad karunga mujhse badke bhi is duniya me bahut kuch hai 
jinhe apne ap par bil kul bhi ghamand nahi hai to mera kisi cheez par ghamand karna bilkul najyaz hai

  
